<subSubSection id="48D355CA8E60FFEE48F75062FF51F87A" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="007606418E60FFEE48F75062FF51F87A" blockId="46.[151,1436,1510,2003]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538E60FFEE48F75062FEC5F897" bold="true" box="[199,352,1870,1895]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Distribution.</emphasis>
Present in the Afrotropical and Oriental regions. Present at Oriental border of the Palaearctic (
<collectingCountry id="78DE46D18E60FFEE48AF505EFF4DF87A" box="[159,232,1906,1930]" name="Nepal" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Nepal</collectingCountry>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="48D355CA8E60FFEE48F750BBFE2BF85E" box="[199,398,1942,1967]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" type="multiple">
<paragraph id="007606418E60FFEE48F750BBFE2BF85E" blockId="46.[151,1436,1510,2003]" box="[199,398,1942,1967]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538E60FFEE48F750BBFEB4F85F" bold="true" box="[199,273,1943,1967]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Hosts.</emphasis>
Unknown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="48D355CA8E60FFEE48F75097FC7DF822" box="[199,984,1978,2003]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" type="type_taxon">
<paragraph id="007606418E60FFEE48F75097FC7DF822" blockId="46.[151,1436,1510,2003]" box="[199,984,1978,2003]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
<emphasis id="32BDDA538E60FFEE48F75097FED1F823" bold="true" box="[199,372,1978,2003]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">World species.</emphasis>
Eleven species are known, four in the 
<collectingRegion id="C20DC8A38E60FFEE4B165096FC71F822" box="[806,980,1978,2002]" country="Democratic Republic of the Congo" name="Orientale" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Oriental region</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
